---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Technical & AV - Renato Moreira"
  description="Sound engineering, audiovisual production and technical operations for festivals, cultural events and international congresses."
>
  <section class="card">
    <h1>Technical & Audiovisual Work</h1>
    <p>
      Technical and audiovisual work across live events, studios, and digital environments.
      Experienced in sound engineering, AV systems, animation, video editing, and
      high-quality image editing for digital and live contexts.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Strong focus on visual post-production, including image editing, color correction,
      compositing, and visual refinement for promotional material, live visuals,
      and multimedia projects.
    </p>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Sound · AV Systems · Image Editing · Animation · Video · Live Events
    </p>
    
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Core Areas</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:14px">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0">Sound Engineering</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Front of House (FOH) and monitor support</li>
          <li>Live sound setup and operation</li>
          <li>Signal routing and system configuration</li>
          <li>Microphone placement and gain structure</li>
          <li>Troubleshooting in live environments</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0">Audiovisual & Event Operations</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>AV setup and operation for congresses and conferences</li>
          <li>Video projection and screen management</li>
          <li>Playback systems and cue-based operation</li>
          <li>Coordination between sound, video and stage teams</li>
          <li>On-site technical problem-solving</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0">Animation & Motion Graphics</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Motion graphics for live visuals and video content</li>
          <li>Animated assets for presentations and events</li>
          <li>Visual adaptation for screens, projection and broadcast</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0">Video Editing</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Editing for event documentation</li>
          <li>Promotional and archival video content</li>
          <li>Sound-synced and presentation-focused edits</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Professional Context</h2>
    <p>
      Renato has worked in high-pressure, time-critical environments involving
      international speakers, large audiences and complex technical chains.
      His role often sits at the intersection of technical execution, communication
      and creative awareness.
    </p>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>International congresses and conferences</li>
      <li>Festivals and cultural events</li>
      <li>Multilingual and multidisciplinary teams</li>
      <li>Tight production schedules</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Approach</h2>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Calm and methodical under pressure</li>
      <li>Detail-oriented with strong situational awareness</li>
      <li>Clear communication with artists and production teams</li>
      <li>Solutions-first mindset</li>
      <li>Sound understanding informed by both art and systems</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Availability</h2>
    <p>
      Available for sound and audiovisual roles in festivals, cultural events,
      international congresses and long- or short-term technical engagements.
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .list {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .list li {
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>